# Capable Wealth: weekly content pipeline schedule (timing reference)
#
# The pipeline is scheduled inside Cowork's built-in "Scheduled" feature, NOT via a
# system crontab. This file just records the intended timing in standard cron syntax
# so it is unambiguous: configure the Cowork Scheduled task to match it.
#
# 4:00 AM every Wednesday, local timezone.
# Generates the upcoming week's drafts so Jared can approve before the following week.
#
# minute hour day-of-month month day-of-week
  0      4    *            *     3
#
# Instruction the scheduled task runs: automation/weekly-pipeline.md
